channel.title: RichScape source is back! (no-longer extinct!)
channel.description:
This source had pretty much gone extinct! However I found an old copy on my computer so I thought i'll post it... all the old links where mainly megaupload, which got taken down.... Time to bring back richscape source around ;) Credits to rich! I only deserve 0.1% for re-uploading it!
LINK TO ORIGINAL THREAD: http://www.rune-server.org/runescape-development/rs2-server/downloads/53745-richscape-v2.html
Source download: http://lnx.lu/0bNv
[B]FEATURES: New Home area, first server to use it as a complete town I believe.
Special attacks, thanks to Delta, also added Specials to most weapons like RuneScape.
Working abyss, glory amulet teleport, and working Runecraft pouches dropped by abyssal monsters
Runecraft pouches work on all altars that require 44+ runecrafting
Working agility skill, with the Maze from RuneScape working
Trawler Minigame
Barrows make-over, with working coffins, and more
Block animation
Updated farming, added Spirit tree patch, and updated the old version
Clue scrolls, dropped by most monsters, with real Clue scroll rewards as RuneScape
Kalphite queen, with same drops as RuneScape
Ice caves, with mithril dragons
Mage Training arena, with working exchange
Replaced Seers teleport with Miscellania
Item dialog
Updated Slayer tower, replaced Dark beasts with Nechryaels, and added a teleport to Dark beasts from Duradeal
Walking Npc's
Shilo Village, with working Skiller minigame, 1500+ Total to play
Working Vengeance
Mage bank, with working sparkling pool, working statue's for god capes
Working mage arena, with levers, axe hut, pirate hut, Chaos elemental, and rouges
Clan wars area
Highscores board
Updated god wars
Working Godsword making, with hilts, and shards
Working Draconic Visage making, with Visage dropped from mithril dragons and anti fire shield
Working crystal keys, and dragon halfs
Working crystal bow animation
TzHaar, with drops just like RuneScape, and working Obby weapons/armor
Hole's in mouth bug fixed, on all hoods, and helmets
Skillcape master, so no more handing out Skillcapes to players
Destory item options, on all Skillcapes/hoods, Fire cape, torso etc, also they are untradable
Suggestion command, so players can suggest updates
Refill Special bar command, and gfx command for admins
Working password command, so players can change they're passes if needed
Fixed many bugs, such as Dark bow dupe, Overlaping animations
Fixed alot of random things, such as added Required for all Skillcapes, and more items
No more getting Bronze long & wooden shield everytime you login, you only get it the first time you ever login
You now get a Character look screen when you login, but you can change your look at the make-over mage
Low train & Mid train portal's at the Start area
New Staff Zone
Updated Dragon area, they have been moved to the wilderness
Fixed Crystal, Karils, and Seercull bows to train Range now instead of Melee
Potions now work
Replaced ::runecraft, you now have to talk to the Zamorak Mage in Edgeville to runecraft
Added a Time clock beside the Name
Working Runecrafting rune's on Magic interface, each rune teleports you to it's own altar
Added Barrows effects
Added Gfx to npc's, such as Barrows, and Abbysal demons
Made it so Administrator's can't trade, drop, or attack other players for Security reasons, but it can simply be fixed
You also need to change alot of 'playerName.equals("Rich")' to your name
Moved dad from Yanille, to Trollheim, to fit it better
Features in V2 from V1
Blue key dungeon
Red key dungeon
Dagannoth Kings
Ancient alter
Backup system (thanks to delta)
Working magic system from with no runes required
Alltome command for owner only
Slayer Tower
Working Farming patches
Barrows Minigame
Torso Minigame
Boss monsters
Fixed cooking & fishing
Working high alching
Shops
Perfect ground item pickuping
Trade Channel
Taverly
Deleted Hammers from Shops
Deleted the "attack" & "duel" right click options to stop dupes
Changed a few Respawn times, & made Npc's hit harder
Deleted alot of unneeded NPC's
Added Requirements to attack NPC's
Added Requirments to wield Weapons
Gave NPC's animation
Made ::yell for Staff only because of spammers
Made dagannoth bones buryable
Raised item cap from 999m to 2bil
Added Herblore shop in taverly & chaos druids drop Herb ingrediants
Deleted the Magic guild dungeon ladder, to stop Noclippers
Replaced Barrows brothers in Yanille dungeon with Infernal mages
Working Bandos GodSword
Working Dark bow
Bandos, Armadyl, 3rd age Melee, 3rd age Mage, Neizotnot Helmet, Dragon Full helm, Skillcapes, Fighter Torso, Black Partyhat, and more, all work.
Media:[/B]
